          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "Step 1",
            "text": "<p>Add your products as a supplier You can integrate your e-commerce software with ours or you can send your product list manually in excel sheet, and we will take care of the rest.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "1655088484fe7cbfa7-1": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "Step 2",
            "text": "<p>Setup Shipping & Prices Before you can go Live and start selling you will need to set the shipping prices for all your products and retail prices you want to collect on orders.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "1655088484fe7cbfa7-2": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "Step 3",
            "text": "<p>Process Your Orders Once an order is placed add the shipping tracking code to your Supplier order dashboard. We already included the shipping costs, so you don't need to worry about collecting any money.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        },
        "ce43fa63-b527-4165-9583-ce13f6734545": {
          "type": "text_block",
          "settings": {
            "enable_image": false,
            "image_width": 650,
            "title": "Step 4",
            "text": "<p>Add Your Inventory Count We have made it easy to add your product inventory to our Supplier dashboard. Upload the latest inventory count or directly integrate your ecommerce store to our App.</p>",
            "button_label": "",
            "button_link": ""
          }
        }
